# Squad Auth

## Dominio

Autenticacao, autorizacao e gestao de usuarios. JWT com access/refresh tokens, RBAC, guards globais, rate limiting em endpoints criticos.

**Fonte de verdade:** PLANO.md secoes 1.2 (Auth e Organizacao), 2.2 (Auth endpoints), 2.3 (Users CRUD)
**Standards:** .claude/standards/07-autenticacao.md
**Fase PLANO:** F2 (construcao) + ownership continuo

---

## Entidades/Recursos sob responsabilidade

| Recurso | Secao PLANO | Descricao |
|---|---|---|
| User model | 1.2 | id, email, name, passwordHash, refreshToken, role, isActive, departmentId |
| Permission model | 1.2 | action, resource, description |
| RolePermission | 1.2 | role + permissionId (pivot) |
| Auth endpoints | 2.2 | register, login, refresh, logout, me |
| Users CRUD | 2.3 | CRUD padrao com RBAC |
| JWT strategies | F2 stories | Access 15min + refresh 7d com rotation |
| Guards globais | F2 stories | JwtAuthGuard + RolesGuard como APP_GUARD |
| Decorators | F2 stories | @CurrentUser, @Roles, @Public |
| Rate limiting | F2 stories | Restritivo em /auth/login e /auth/register |

